ing: 2 pounds kielbasa sausage, sliced into 1/2 inch pieces
n: Island Kielbasa in a Slow Cooker
des: "My mother gave this recipe to me and it is a big hit at parties and potlucks. You never have to bring home any leftovers!"
ins:
Place the sausage, ketchup, sugar and pineapple in the slow cooker and mix together.
Cook on low setting for 5 to 6 hours, until sausage is cooked through.
